{"tid":1881481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"翠雅山房隔離    康美樓撤離戶：一日三餐生活幾好","createTime":"2020-02-15T14:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T11:51:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3aed284d773a8e85059fde1b31f918f5b75a0ffd","tid":1881481,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XixuY7zBYiIRZ4ebBO7qrA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200215a143225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXixuY7zBYiIRZ4ebBO7qrA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200215a143225.jpg&h=9fed0216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n漏夜撤離接受檢役的101名青衣長康邨康美樓A07單位居民，經過5日隔離後，全部人對新型冠狀病毒肺炎測試呈陰性反應，今日離開隔離營，中午過後返抵家園。<br />\n<br />\n居於康美樓2407室的包先生，返抵家門前接受訪問時表示，與妻子在坐落美孚新邨附近饒宗頤文化館內的翠雅山房隔離。他形容接受隔離期間生活幾好，一日早午晚供應三餐，探兩次熱，期間以睇電視及打遊戲機消磨時間。檢疫期間心情不緊張，因知道自己身體無事。<br />\n<br />\n表明家中無改裝渠管的包先生，回想起漏夜撤離的情景時坦言，當時也感到有點緊張。包先生認為回家較舒服，因不用再被困著，沒有自由。而回家首要是執屋和繼續做消毒和清潔工作。"},{"pid":"cd78825aa365923e06d0f10d082043caf7b400c3","tid":1881481,"uid":175659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"如果有習慣一日一丁既巴打被捉入去可以點生存"},{"pid":"8127f3cf07eddc5664d8f88739f5b384f773ccf2","tid":1881481,"uid":20363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd78825aa365923e06d0f10d082043caf7b400c3","tid":1881481,"uid":175659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"如果有習慣一日一丁既巴打被捉入去可以點生存"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"有手機架嘛！？"},{"pid":"07355ce7965440766b8ed34a52625d5cf70e0c13","tid":1881481,"uid":159281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"翠雅山房環境真係幾好，d房夠大，係上去條路隔涉d"},{"pid":"5b177624b09e65b4fe60cb9f41dc47372179478d","tid":1881481,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T16:28:35.000Z","msg":"好想永久隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />間房靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好食好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41a3a15aba160bb26c1bf4baf79623a78c8cd66","tid":1881481,"uid":135957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:39:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f725f5947d1e2351387a1da8110000e5be1d7d43","tid":1881481,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"隔離5日??<br />\n<br />\n屌你, 唔係14日咩?"},{"pid":"9dcfa07207ad728366d17d01630562917e17ab46","tid":1881481,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f725f5947d1e2351387a1da8110000e5be1d7d43","tid":1881481,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"隔離5日??<br />\n<br />\n屌你, 唔係14日咩?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"驗左係陰性"},{"pid":"7304d8cd21eae70459a2657b89d27e537733d6fa","tid":1881481,"uid":33609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dcfa07207ad728366d17d01630562917e17ab46","tid":1881481,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f725f5947d1e2351387a1da8110000e5be1d7d43","tid":1881481,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"隔離5日??<br />\n<br />\n屌你, 唔係14日咩?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"驗左係陰性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"未夠14 日喎   佢前5日假陰性第6日發出黎咪仆晒街"},{"pid":"efe4ddb7fbdbf2095f7b34b93c27c1e990dd497a","tid":1881481,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd78825aa365923e06d0f10d082043caf7b400c3","tid":1881481,"uid":175659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:40:45.000Z","msg":"如果有習慣一日一丁既巴打被捉入去可以點生存"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"